<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center mb-3">
    <div class="col-8 text-center bg-dark rounded p-3 border border-3 border-primary text-light" >
      <h1>Event Schedule</h1>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card shadow mb-3">
  <div class="card-header">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <h2 class="mb-0">Volunteer Night</h2>
      <h4 class="mb-0">Wednesday Sept. 24</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row mt-3">
      <div class="text-start text-primary">
        <ul>
          <li>Gate opens at 5pm</li>
          <li>Only for <%= Time.zone.now.year - 1 %> and <%= Time.zone.now.year %> Officers, committee volunteers, and ticket tent volunteers</li>
          <li>No formal plans for food, bring your own and have a relaxing evening!</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card shadow mb-3">
  <div class="card-header">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <h2 class="mb-0">Camp Dale</h2>
      <h4 class="mb-0">Thursday Sept. 25</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row mt-3">
      <div class="text-start text-primary">
        <ul>
          <li>Camp is open to all members after 4pm</li> 
          <li>Continuing the Thursday tradition</li>
          <li>Please donate $20 to cover camp costs (payable to the club, standard payment options)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card shadow mb-3">
  <div class="card-header">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <h2 class="mb-0">Friday Night Lights</h2>
      <h4 class="mb-0">Friday Sept. 26</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row mt-3">
      <div class="text-start text-primary">
        <ul>
          <li>Open to all members</li>
          <li>Come help us and our commercial brewery friends setup and get ready for BrewFest!</li> 
          <li>Shrimp Boil/Gumbo will be available for $15, but food tickets are limited.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card shadow mb-3">
  <div class="card-header">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center">
      <h2 class="mb-0">Brew Fest</h2>
      <h4 class="mb-0">Saturday Sept. 27</h4>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row mt-3">
      <div class="text-start text-primary">
        <ul>
          <li>12pm - 6pm</li> 
          <li>Catered mains to be announced soon!</li> 
          <li>Bring a side or dessert for the potluck!</li>
          <li>Camping is open to all members</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>